WEBVTT

01:13.390 --> 01:14.023
This city.

01:15.189 --> 01:16.889
What can I tell you about the city?

01:17.889 --> 01:18.589
New York.

01:19.521 --> 01:21.055
A place where the men work hard

01:21.055 --> 01:23.122
and the dames well,

01:23.122 --> 01:24.521
they do what it is they do.

01:25.755 --> 01:26.920
The lively city hides

01:26.920 --> 01:28.588
the underbelly that runs

01:28.588 --> 01:29.221
through the gutters

01:29.221 --> 01:30.454
and the smoke filled streets.

01:31.387 --> 01:32.621
That's where I come into play.

01:33.620 --> 01:36.020
My name is Detective Sal Pelletier,

01:36.020 --> 01:38.353
when I tell you I seen it all.

01:39.286 --> 01:42.386
I mean, I seen it all, from

01:43.686 --> 01:43.985
the mobsters to the whores,

01:43.985 --> 01:45.419
the crooked bankers to the killers

01:45.419 --> 01:46.652
that hide in the shadows,

01:46.652 --> 01:47.551
waiting to strike

01:47.551 --> 01:49.051
when an opportunity appears.

01:50.418 --> 01:51.651
Sometimes I look out of

01:51.651 --> 01:52.884
my window at this city

01:53.851 --> 01:55.317
and then I look up at the sky

01:55.317 --> 01:56.984
and I see dark clouds,

01:56.984 --> 02:00.050
and all I can think is that God himself

02:00.050 --> 02:01.283
is trying to hide this city

02:01.283 --> 02:02.350
from his own eyes.

02:03.550 --> 02:04.083
Oh, yeah,

02:05.150 --> 02:06.583
I seen it all, alright.

02:08.249 --> 02:10.449
But tonight's story doesn't take place

02:10.449 --> 02:12.615
in some mobster's warehouse

02:12.615 --> 02:14.648
or some rundown bar

02:14.648 --> 02:15.815
full of the unfortunates

02:15.881 --> 02:16.781
of this great city.

02:17.781 --> 02:19.048
Our story takes place

02:19.048 --> 02:20.381
in the suburbs of New York,

02:21.214 --> 02:23.579
a nice street, a middle-class

02:23.579 --> 02:25.447
household with a perfect lawn

02:25.447 --> 02:28.146
and perfectly respectable residents.

02:29.079 --> 02:30.478
But as we know all too well,

02:31.313 --> 02:32.646
darkness can hide

02:32.646 --> 02:33.978
in the lightest of places.

02:35.412 --> 02:37.212
So let me tell you about Veronica.

02:38.078 --> 02:39.545
Veronica, Smart.

02:39.545 --> 02:41.845
Beautiful, intelligent,

02:42.611 --> 02:44.111
but with a life that will be anything

02:44.111 --> 02:45.178
but respectable.

02:46.377 --> 02:48.110
Veronica was married to Cliff see.

02:48.810 --> 02:49.610
They met when they were

02:49.610 --> 02:50.942
just college sweethearts.

02:51.910 --> 02:53.410
He'd done all right for himself

02:54.076 --> 02:55.709
up in the high rises of work

02:56.343 --> 02:58.042
with a love of a good woman at home.

02:59.109 --> 03:01.142
But temptation can hide around

03:01.142 --> 03:02.842
any corner of this great city.

03:03.508 --> 03:04.042
And Cliff.

03:05.108 --> 03:06.441
Well, Cliff had succumbed

03:06.441 --> 03:07.675
to the ways of a woman

03:07.675 --> 03:08.674
who wasn't his wife.

03:10.041 --> 03:12.207
So that's where we meet them.

03:13.207 --> 03:14.240
That's where we meet her.

03:14.907 --> 03:16.007
Veronica Smart.

03:17.140 --> 03:21.173
Welcome to the world of NOIR.

05:19.090 --> 05:23.523
