as the bad guy, Jimmy.

1:08:56.148 --> 1:08:58.049
I'm just doing my best to guide you.

1:08:58.049 --> 1:08:59.515
Guide me?

1:09:00.749 --> 1:09:01.815
You mean destroy me.

1:09:02.582 --> 1:09:04.215
You know, I'd have more respect

1:09:04.215 --> 1:09:05.615
if you told me that you hated me.

1:09:05.648 --> 1:09:06.880
I don't hate you Jimmy.

1:09:07.781 --> 1:09:09.081
I just know what's best for you.

1:09:10.346 --> 1:09:11.147
You don't even know

1:09:11.147 --> 1:09:12.246
what's best for yourself.

1:09:13.147 --> 1:09:13.746
Jimmy!

1:09:13.746 --> 1:09:15.513
Get back here now!

1:09:18.612 --> 1:09:20.646
Veronica was like a whirlwind,

1:09:20.646 --> 1:09:23.078
she was already leaving her mark

1:09:23.211 --> 1:09:24.578
and what a mark it was.

1:09:25.545 --> 1:09:27.444
But that night as clouds

1:09:27.444 --> 1:09:28.944
rolled over the city,

1:09:28.944 --> 1:09:33.011
things will take a turn, a dark turn

1:09:33.011 --> 1:09:35.411
that will change everything.

1:09:40.309 --> 1:09:41.010
It's nice, isn't it.

1:09:42.976 --> 1:09:44.143
Us being able to do this.

1:09:45.876 --> 1:09:46.809
These past few weeks with you

1:09:46.809 --> 1:09:48.408
have been incredible Veronica.

1:09:48.908 --> 1:09:51.309
They sure have and you're right,

1:09:52.342 --> 1:09:53.242
it is nice.

1:09:54.407 --> 1:09:55.308
I just wish it could be

1:09:55.308 --> 1:09:57.141
like this all the time.

1:09:57.441 --> 1:09:57.808
Yeah.

1:09:59.341 --> 1:10:00.207
Wake up in the morning,

1:10:00.207 --> 1:10:01.474
take a ride on my bike

1:10:01.474 --> 1:10:02.374
wherever you want to go.

1:10:02.874 --> 1:10:03.639
Hollywood.

1:10:03.740 --> 1:10:04.874
Hollywood, it is.

1:10:05.940 --> 1:10:07.073
We could watch the sunset

1:10:07.073 --> 1:10:08.306
over the City of Angels.

1:10:10.206 --> 1:10:13.106
We could hold each other tightly wrapped

1:10:13.106 --> 1:10:15.039
up, nice and warm in a blanket.

1:10:21.737 --> 1:10:22.405
Do you think it could

1:10:22.405 --> 1:10:23.404
ever happen, Veronica?

1:10:25.671 --> 1:10:27.271
That you leave Cliff.

1:10:28.637 --> 1:10:31.270
If I had the money, the security.

1:10:32.969 --> 1:10:34.403
I would in a heartbeat Jimmy.

1:10:35.236 --> 1:10:36.436
I have a little saved.

1:10:37.403 --> 1:10:38.436
That's very sweet,

1:10:39.402 --> 1:10:40.469
but a little saved,

1:10:40.469 --> 1:10:42.135
won't get us very far.

1:10:43.135 --> 1:10:44.702
If only Cliff wasn't around.

1:10:45.835 --> 1:10:46.835
Yeah.

1:10:48.268 --> 1:10:49.101
If only.

1:10:55.300 --> 1:10:56.567
I don't think you're old enough

1:10:56.567 --> 1:10:57.833
to be drinking my liquor.

1:10:58.133 --> 1:10:59.032
Who the hell are you?

1:10:59.366 --> 1:11:00.398
The man of the house.

1:11:00.532 --> 1:11:01.898
Oh, Mr. Smart.

1:11:02.266 --> 1:11:05.066
Wait a minute, I know you,

1:11:05.365 --> 1:11:06.032
Oh, shit!

1:11:06.065 --> 1:11:07.698
it's you, the kid with the bat.

1:11:07.798 --> 1:11:08.398
Mister I didn't know

1:11:08.398 --> 1:11:09.298
you were Veronica's husband.

1:11:09.665 --> 1:11:10.465
You are dead!

1:11:10.998 --> 1:11:14.231
Get the hell of him Mr Smart, run Riff!

1:11:14.231 --> 1:11:15.364
Why are you in my house?

1:11:15.697 --> 1:11:16.531
We know your wife.

1:11:16.531 --> 1:11:17.864
She's teaching us, asking.

1:11:17.864 --> 1:11:18.830
Where's my wife?

1:11:19.264 --> 1:11:19.964
She's upstairs.

1:11:19.964 --> 1:11:20.996
Do you want me to go get her?

1:11:21.030 --> 1:11:21.930
Is she alone?

1:11:21.930 --> 1:11:22.830
Alone?

1:11:22.830 --> 1:11:25.196
Is my wife alone?

1:11:27.329 --> 1:11:28.496
Get the hell out of my house.

1:11:28.629 --> 1:11:31.129
Now, and you tell your friend

1:11:31.162 --> 1:11:33.662
I'll be seeing you again Riff, real soon.

1:11:42.894 --> 1:11:43.660
What the hell is this?

1:11:44.559 --> 1:11:47.559
Cliff, I didn't expect you home tonight.

1:11:47.826 --> 1:11:48.626
So I see.

1:11:50.425 --> 1:11:51.425
So when I'm gone, you

1:11:52.493 --> 1:11:54.291
have kids over to get drunk in my house.

1:11:55.725 --> 1:11:57.291
These are your new......

1:11:57.291 --> 1:11:58.425
friends?

1:11:58.657 --> 1:11:59.791
I told you Cliff,

1:12:00.325 --> 1:12:02.291
I'm giving them acting lessons.

1:12:02.458 --> 1:12:02.924
Oh, yeah.

1:12:04.091 --> 1:12:04.724
So what's this?

1:12:05.991 --> 1:12:07.591
Some kind of love scene

1:12:08.057 --> 1:12:08.724
in my bed?

1:12:09.057 --> 1:12:09.790
Excuse me?

1:12:09.790 --> 1:12:11.057
Jimmy, you should go.

1:12:11.790 --> 1:12:12.290
Yeah, Jimmy,

1:12:13.790 --> 1:12:16.989
maybe you should leave my bedroom,

1:12:18.022 --> 1:12:19.489
that I share with my wife.

1:12:19.522 --> 1:12:21.589
We were just talking, must

1:12:21.589 --> 1:12:22.855
you act like such a brute.

1:12:22.855 --> 1:12:25.121
Mr Smart, Veronica and I....

1:12:25.588 --> 1:12:28.321
There ain't no Veronica and you kid, now

1:12:28.421 --> 1:12:30.353
run home like a good little boy.

1:12:30.521 --> 1:12:31.187
Cliff.

1:12:33.387 --> 1:12:35.154
Get out of my house.

1:12:37.787 --> 1:12:40.886
I said, get out of my house.

1:12:44.652 --> 1:12:45.286
What's wrong?

1:12:45.985 --> 1:12:47.052
Do you not hear too good?

1:12:47.619 --> 1:12:49.552
I said, get out of my house.

1:12:51.585 --> 1:12:52.585
Cliff!

1:12:52.585 --> 1:12:56.584
Stop it, stop it.

1:13:02.916 --> 1:13:04.250
You've been looking at my wife?

1:13:04.816 --> 1:13:05.416
Touching her?

1:13:06.849 --> 1:13:08.582
If you're man enough to go near her,

1:13:09.148 --> 1:13:10.582
you're man enough to fight me.

1:13:10.982 --> 1:13:11.615
Cliff!

1:13:11.615 --> 1:13:12.215
If you don't leave him alone

1:13:12.215 --> 1:13:13.348
I'm going to call the police.

1:13:13.548 --> 1:13:14.682
I know your type, Jimmy.

1:13:15.115 --> 1:13:16.281
Oh, you think you can get

1:13:16.281 --> 1:13:17.415
what you want from her. Huh?

1:13:18.214 --> 1:13:19.314
Maybe you should stick

1:13:19.514 --> 1:13:21.114
to the slum side of town

1:13:21.114 --> 1:13:21.947
because I don't ever want

1:13:21.947 --> 1:13:23.114
to see you around here again.

1:13:25.180 --> 1:13:26.612
I'm going alright .

1:13:28.580 --> 1:13:29.046
I'm going.

1:13:29.680 --> 1:13:31.079
Stay away from my wife, Jimmy.

1:13:31.579 --> 1:13:33.346
Or I'll rip you to pieces,

1:13:33.346 --> 1:13:35.012
limb by limb,

1:13:35.012 --> 1:13:36.412
do we understand each other?

1:13:41.545 --> 1:13:42.745
How dare you?

1:13:43.344 --> 1:13:44.778
What the hell do you think you're doing?

1:13:44.778 --> 1:13:45.511
Don't.

1:13:46.977 --> 1:13:47.544
Don't talk to me.

1:13:47.577 --> 1:13:49.943
We were just working Cliff.

1:13:49.943 --> 1:13:51.277
And the kids downstairs?

1:13:51.277 --> 1:13:52.043
Students.

1:13:52.410 --> 1:13:53.443
The boy that attacked me

1:13:53.443 --> 1:13:55.043
with the bat, that was him

1:13:55.743 --> 1:13:57.643
that sewer rat was in my living room.

1:13:57.643 --> 1:13:59.776
But I'm sure he didn't know who you were.

1:14:00.041 --> 1:14:01.242
He could have killed me

1:14:01.242 --> 1:14:02.609
and what would you have done then, huh?

1:14:03.208 --> 1:14:04.475
One of your students attacks

1:14:04.475 --> 1:14:06.775
your husband, bashes his skull in.

1:14:06.775 --> 1:14:09.474
Jesus, what kind of company do you keep?

1:14:09.474 --> 1:14:11.207
Cliff wait.

1:14:11.207 --> 1:14:12.574
Do you want me divorce you,

1:14:12.574 --> 1:14:13.240
leave you with nothing?

1:14:13.240 --> 1:14:17.107
No Cliff, you're getting it all wrong.

1:14:22.106 --> 1:14:22.606
Good night,

1:14:23.806 --> 1:14:24.639
my dear wife.

1:14:40.270 --> 1:14:41.837
Now, here is the thing.

1:14:42.503 --> 1:14:43.736
This dame ain't going to do

1:14:43.736 --> 1:14:44.503
well in poverty.

1:14:45.136 --> 1:14:47.068
Poor is not a style she wears well.

1:14:47.603 --> 1:14:49.335
Well, this is the part

1:14:49.335 --> 1:14:51.369
you may not believe, but I assure you

1:14:51.502 --> 1:14:53.002
every word is true.

1:14:53.868 --> 1:14:55.368
Veronica slammed her face

1:14:55.368 --> 1:14:56.535
against the hard wall.

1:14:58.334 --> 1:14:59.168
Why?

1:14:59.934 --> 1:15:01.666
Well, after a quick phone

1:15:01.666 --> 1:15:03.700
call to a distraught Jimmy and a late

1:15:03.700 --> 1:15:04.700
night meeting arranged,

1:15:05.267 --> 1:15:06.800
a bruise would sell Veronica's

1:15:06.800 --> 1:15:08.067
story perfectly.

1:15:09.266 --> 1:15:09.866
Oh, God.

1:15:09.900 --> 1:15:12.032
Jimmy, Jimmy, are you OK?

1:15:12.166 --> 1:15:13.232
Son of a bitch.

1:15:14.732 --> 1:15:16.565
Your face, what did he do to your face?

1:15:16.965 --> 1:15:17.965
I told you, Jimmy.

1:15:18.132 --> 1:15:20.165
He's a violent brute of a man.

1:15:20.165 --> 1:15:21.931
I never wanted you to get hurt.

1:15:22.098 --> 1:15:23.031
Forget about me.

1:15:23.065 --> 1:15:24.898
We need to get you away from him.

1:15:24.931 --> 1:15:26.564
He can't do this to you.

1:15:26.831 --> 1:15:27.531
But how?

1:15:27.597 --> 1:15:29.897
Just, just leave him.

1:15:29.930 --> 1:15:31.463
Who cares if he leaves you with nothing?

1:15:31.496 --> 1:15:32.330
You have me.

1:15:32.362 --> 1:15:33.330
We have each other.

1:15:33.630 --> 1:15:34.830
Jimmy, you're young.

1:15:35.096 --> 1:15:36.329
You don't understand

1:15:36.329 --> 1:15:37.862
how much living can cost.

1:15:38.429 --> 1:15:40.462
We would be broke, unhappy

1:15:40.462 --> 1:15:42.594
and resenting each other in no time.

1:15:43.862 --> 1:15:44.827
Face it Jimmy.

1:15:45.562 --> 1:15:47.728
I'm stuck with him until my dying day.

1:15:47.761 --> 1:15:48.094
No.

1:15:49.494 --> 1:15:51.494
No, we have to think of another way.

1:15:51.627 --> 1:15:53.460
I can't live another day without you.

1:15:56.427 --> 1:15:57.160
I love you.

1:15:58.893 --> 1:15:59.526
Jimmy.

1:15:59.526 --> 1:16:01.893
Do you love me?

1:16:03.626 --> 1:16:05.559
Everything about this is wrong,

1:16:05.559 --> 1:16:08.225
and yet I have never felt more safe

1:16:08.225 --> 1:16:10.558
in anyone's arms as I do in yours.

1:16:10.991 --> 1:16:12.391
I want to go back there and show him

1:16:12.391 --> 1:16:13.458
who's the man around here.

1:16:16.023 --> 1:16:16.457
Jimmy,

1:16:18.224 --> 1:16:19.224
I just had a thought.

1:16:20.490 --> 1:16:21.457
A horrible thought.

1:16:22.723 --> 1:16:23.755
What is it, Veronica?

1:16:23.755 --> 1:16:24.255
Tell me.

1:16:25.989 --> 1:16:26.523
I couldn't.

1:16:27.389 --> 1:16:28.255
It's too awful.

1:16:28.255 --> 1:16:29.689
Yes, you can just

1:16:30.922 --> 1:16:31.621
just say it.

1:16:33.755 --> 1:16:35.455
Well, the way I see it

1:16:35.487 --> 1:16:37.688
is that only Cliff and the lack of money

1:16:37.688 --> 1:16:39.888
stands in the way of true happiness.

1:16:40.821 --> 1:16:41.287
OK.

1:16:42.487 --> 1:16:43.887
But if Cliff wasn't around,

1:16:43.887 --> 1:16:48.287
if Cliff died, I would get everything.

1:16:48.920 --> 1:16:50.420
We would have everything

1:16:50.420 --> 1:16:51.153
we need to have the

1:16:51.153 --> 1:16:52.452
perfect life together.

1:16:52.452 --> 1:16:53.818
But he isn't going anywhere.

1:16:53.852 --> 1:16:54.786
You saw him.

1:16:55.052 --> 1:16:56.619
He's as strong as an ox.

1:16:59.418 --> 1:17:00.318
Jimmy, I could pay,

1:17:01.218 --> 1:17:03.584
I could pay anyone who helps.

1:17:03.984 --> 1:17:05.151
I mean, think about it, Jimmy.

1:17:05.151 --> 1:17:06.084
This is New York.

1:17:06.117 --> 1:17:08.184
People die all the time.

1:17:08.784 --> 1:17:09.550
We could say that

1:17:09.550 --> 1:17:11.117
it was a robbery gone bad.

1:17:11.916 --> 1:17:13.350
Nobody would suspect you.

1:17:13.716 --> 1:17:14.350
Why would they?

1:17:14.350 --> 1:17:15.516
Nobody knows about us

1:17:15.516 --> 1:17:16.483
other than those two.

1:17:16.683 --> 1:17:19.316
And they won't say a word.

1:17:19.316 --> 1:17:20.916
I will make sure of that.

1:17:22.082 --> 1:17:23.082
Think about it, Jimmy.

1:17:24.182 --> 1:17:25.482
Think about it, this could work,

1:17:25.482 --> 1:17:26.615
we could be free.

1:17:27.548 --> 1:17:28.981
What are you saying, Veronica?

1:17:30.581 --> 1:17:30.981
Jimmy,

1:17:33.147 --> 1:17:34.514
I want you to kill my husband.

1:17:36.180 --> 1:17:39.180
(Thunder Crashes)

1:18:01.743 --> 1:18:03.876
What's all this?

1:18:03.876 --> 1:18:05.175
I did you the favour of packing

1:18:05.175 --> 1:18:06.243
your bags for you baby?

1:18:07.043 --> 1:18:08.709
You're absurd Cliff.

1:18:08.709 --> 1:18:10.076
Look, I don't want to hear it Veronica,

1:18:10.675 --> 1:18:12.175
seeing you sat on our bed with

1:18:12.175 --> 1:18:13.275
that kid was one thing,

1:18:13.842 --> 1:18:14.907
but it was the look in your eyes

1:18:14.907 --> 1:18:15.907
that told me everything.

1:18:16.141 --> 1:18:17.508
What are you talking about?

1:18:17.641 --> 1:18:19.641
The betrayal was in your eyes.

1:18:20.141 --> 1:18:21.108
I saw it the moment

1:18:21.108 --> 1:18:22.007
I walked in the bedroom.

1:18:22.141 --> 1:18:24.207
Oh, you're talking in circles Cliff.

1:18:24.207 --> 1:18:25.474
Why aren't you listening to me!

1:18:25.474 --> 1:18:26.573
Cliff!

1:18:26.573 --> 1:18:27.907
I want you gone Veronica.

1:18:28.040 --> 1:18:29.606
I am done.

1:18:29.606 --> 1:18:31.906
You lie, all you do is lie.

1:18:31.906 --> 1:18:33.739
I can't trust you, I can't trust a word

1:18:33.739 --> 1:18:34.839
that comes out of your mouth.

1:18:35.339 --> 1:18:36.939
You strung me along for years.

1:18:37.072 --> 1:18:38.239
You never had any intention

1:18:38.239 --> 1:18:39.105
of becoming a mother.

1:18:39.371 --> 1:18:40.172
I see that now.

1:18:40.172 --> 1:18:42.237
Now you're painting yourself

1:18:42.237 --> 1:18:44.071
as a victim Cliff.

1:18:44.071 --> 1:18:45.471
Again, you cheated.

1:18:45.504 --> 1:18:46.837
This isn't about that.

1:18:46.837 --> 1:18:49.103
Look I haven't got a future with you.

1:18:49.469 --> 1:18:51.137
I see that now baby, you've made

1:18:51.137 --> 1:18:52.237
that perfectly clear.

1:18:52.670 --> 1:18:54.370
You son of a bitch.

1:18:54.903 --> 1:18:55.903
Well if you think I'm

1:18:55.903 --> 1:18:57.503
walking away from this marriage

1:18:57.503 --> 1:19:00.036
with nothing but a few cases of clothing?

1:19:00.236 --> 1:19:01.202
Well, there it is.

1:19:01.369 --> 1:19:03.169
Money, belongings and things.

1:19:03.169 --> 1:19:04.135
That's all you care about,

1:19:04.135 --> 1:19:04.902
right, Veronica?

1:19:05.002 --> 1:19:06.335
You won't get away with this.

1:19:06.901 --> 1:19:08.768
Big words, but we both know that I will.

1:19:09.101 --> 1:19:11.068
You are making a mistake, Cliff.

1:19:12.134 --> 1:19:13.567
You know, um.

1:19:13.567 --> 1:19:14.200
That

1:19:15.367 --> 1:19:20.532
kid, Riff, the kid that was in my house.

1:19:21.366 --> 1:19:22.066
What about him?

1:19:22.766 --> 1:19:27.332
Look, just a pretty small world ain't it.

1:19:29.332 --> 1:19:30.532
Just one of the kids

1:19:30.532 --> 1:19:32.465
that you've been hopelessly

1:19:32.998 --> 1:19:34.464
flaunting yourself in front of

1:19:34.464 --> 1:19:36.364
like some cheap whore.

1:19:37.331 --> 1:19:38.297
Just happens to be

1:19:38.297 --> 1:19:39.297
the kid who attacks me.

1:19:40.364 --> 1:19:41.397
What are you saying?

1:19:43.097 --> 1:19:44.463
Did you put him up to that Veronica?

1:19:45.530 --> 1:19:45.996
God,

1:19:47.696 --> 1:19:49.296
how could you even think that?

1:19:49.929 --> 1:19:50.228
Oh,

1:19:51.329 --> 1:19:52.462
well, here we go.

1:19:53.395 --> 1:19:54.762
Bring on the tears.

1:19:55.862 --> 1:19:56.728
Why don't you save them

1:19:56.728 --> 1:19:58.094
for one of your teenage lovers?

1:19:58.094 --> 1:19:59.827
I'm sure they'll eat em up.

1:19:59.827 --> 1:20:02.427
You're insane, sick,

1:20:02.427 --> 1:20:03.661
thinking that I would

1:20:03.661 --> 1:20:04.660
sleep with a student.

1:20:04.960 --> 1:20:05.594
You know, the fact

1:20:05.594 --> 1:20:06.827
that you even suggested

1:20:06.827 --> 1:20:09.393
it says more about you.

1:20:09.460 --> 1:20:10.925
Well, I know you, Veronica,

1:20:10.925 --> 1:20:12.326
and I know when you lie.

1:20:12.359 --> 1:20:13.726
You cannot divorce me.

1:20:13.893 --> 1:20:15.126
Oh, really?

1:20:15.526 --> 1:20:16.725
Why don't you watch me?

1:20:17.159 --> 1:20:18.725
Cliff, I never slept with anyone else.

1:20:18.725 --> 1:20:19.592
Lies!

1:20:19.592 --> 1:20:21.192
I had nothing to do with Riffs attack.

1:20:21.192 --> 1:20:21.758
Lies!

1:20:22.091 --> 1:20:22.891
Please wait.

1:20:23.058 --> 1:20:24.724
We just ,we got to talk.

1:20:25.023 --> 1:20:26.224
I'm done talking.

1:20:26.224 --> 1:20:27.157
No Cliff, please.

1:20:27.157 --> 1:20:28.523
I said I'm done Veronica.

1:20:28.523 --> 1:20:29.290
Please Cliff, I have

1:20:29.290 --> 1:20:30.457
something to tell you.

1:20:30.924 --> 1:20:34.255
