1:22:16.743 --> 1:22:17.743
when I was a teenager.

1:22:20.842 --> 1:22:24.475
And one day, out of the blue,

1:22:27.741 --> 1:22:28.341
I found out she got

1:22:28.341 --> 1:22:29.341
