1:23:05.370 --> 1:23:08.769
Oh, yeah, what plans?

1:23:10.536 --> 1:23:12.934
Plans. Plans.

1:23:13.735 --> 1:23:15.468
You're lliving in La La Land, Jimmy.

1:23:16.235 --> 1:23:17.434
