1:25:28.084 --> 1:25:30.184
I've never felt so unwanted before.

1:25:31.317 --> 1:25:33.483
I remember crying my bedroom days

1:25:33.483 --> 1:25:35.782
just waiting for her to return.

1:25:36.183 --> 1:25:38.316
He went on to say how he hated his

1:25:38.316 --> 1:25:39.483
