1:26:32.309 --> 1:26:33.041
Of course I do.

1:26:34.309 --> 1:26:35.142
If it's right.

1:26:36.875 --> 1:26:37.641
It's forever.

1:26:39.708 --> 1:26:40.608
Then maybe it's true.

1:26:42.308 --> 1:26:43.441
Maybe there is one

1:26:43.441 --> 1:26:44.773
perfect person out there,

1:26:44.773 --> 1:26:46.174
I mean, I know I believe that.

1:26:47.207 --> 1:26:48.639
I know that I hurt so much

1:26:48.639 --> 1:26:50.005
