1:26:50.340 --> 1:26:51.473
An unbearable pain.

1:26:53.005 --> 1:26:54.673
That has to mean something, right?

1:26:57.371 --> 1:26:58.839
That's love, Jimmy,

1:26:59.805 --> 1:27:01.138
