1:27:01.405 --> 1:27:03.205
Jimmy was feeling the pain of love,

1:27:03.205 --> 1:27:03.737
alright.

1:27:04.737 --> 1:27:06.671
All he saw was her.

1:27:07.304 --> 1:27:08.571
All I see is you.

1:27:09.537 --> 1:27:11.004
And all I see is you Jimmy.

1:27:11.404 --> 1:27:13.837
And as the sun started

1:27:13.837 --> 1:27:15.436
