1:28:58.089 --> 1:28:59.523
A father?

1:29:00.589 --> 1:29:02.489
We can do this Jimmy.

1:29:02.489 --> 1:29:06.088
You, me, our child, a family,

1:29:06.621 --> 1:29:07.788
a family, Jimmy.

1:29:08.388 --> 1:29:10.188
I know how much you've always

1:29:10.188 --> 1:29:12.821
